<p>While Lebeau’s defenses don’t typically rank high in turnovers, they do a great job at keeping
    opponents from moving the ball down the field and into the endzone. John Madden once said, “The best way to gain
    more yards is advance the ball down the field from the line of scrimmage.” No truer words have ever been spoken, and
    Lebeau has a history of limiting the opponent’s yards and points. You might want to consider your matchups for any
    games your players have against the Titans in 2017.</p>